### Books REST API — Chapter 12 (hardened)
### Use VS Code "REST Client" or Postman.

@host  = http://localhost:8000
@token = paste-the-access_token-here

# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. Health — shows current security posture
# ---------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{host}}/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# 2. Login (rate-limited 5 / 60s by default)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### As admin
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "admin@books.test", "password": "password" }

### As member
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "member@books.test", "password": "password" }

### Wrong password — repeat 6 times to trigger 429 Too Many Requests
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "admin@books.test", "password": "wrong" }

# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# 3. XSS hygiene — JSON output is HEX-tag-encoded
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### Try to store an XSS payload (allowed string, but rendered safely on output)
POST {{host}}/api/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJib29rcy1hcGkiLCJzdWIiOjEsImlhdCI6MTc4MTA2NTEyNCwiZXhwIjoxNzgxMDY4NzI0LCJyb2xlIjoiYWRtaW4iLCJlbWFpbCI6ImFkbWluQGJvb2tzLnRlc3QifQ.wXZe9VCXOK-8YFRlEmKVnVB5tAyRqfqEllMeMgyFgGI

{
  "title":  "<script>alert('xss')</script>",
  "author": "Attacker",
  "year":   2024
}

### Read it back — observe < > in the JSON instead of < >
GET {{host}}/api/books

# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# 4. IDOR — owner-or-admin only
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### As member, try to update a book NOT created by you (expect 403)
PUT {{host}}/api/books/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJib29rcy1hcGkiLCJzdWIiOjIsImlhdCI6MTc4MTA2NTMxNSwiZXhwIjoxNzgxMDY4OTE1LCJyb2xlIjoibWVtYmVyIiwiZW1haWwiOiJtZW1iZXJAYm9va3MudGVzdCJ9.iRE-zv7jWkt3xuS_d6NXXLWz5uZDkKgTi52XzBFnoXI

{ "title": "Hijacked" }

### As admin, the same call succeeds (200)
PUT {{host}}/api/books/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJib29rcy1hcGkiLCJzdWIiOjEsImlhdCI6MTc4MTA2NTEyNCwiZXhwIjoxNzgxMDY4NzI0LCJyb2xlIjoiYWRtaW4iLCJlbWFpbCI6ImFkbWluQGJvb2tzLnRlc3QifQ.wXZe9VCXOK-8YFRlEmKVnVB5tAyRqfqEllMeMgyFgGI

{ "genre": "Software Craftsmanship" }

# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# 5. Validation — server rejects bad inputs (400)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### Year out of range
POST {{host}}/api/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJib29rcy1hcGkiLCJzdWIiOjEsImlhdCI6MTc4MTA2MzMwOSwiZXhwIjoxNzgxMDY2OTA5LCJyb2xlIjoiYWRtaW4iLCJlbWFpbCI6ImFkbWluQGJvb2tzLnRlc3QifQ.UQgLb9jfmxQQPN_oFphv6zKW6AQU_J36VcB_mBdalWI

{ "title": "Future Book", "author": "Time Traveller", "year": 9999 }

### Title too long (> 200 chars)
POST {{host}}/api/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJib29rcy1hcGkiLCJzdWIiOjEsImlhdCI6MTc4MTA2MzMwOSwiZXhwIjoxNzgxMDY2OTA5LCJyb2xlIjoiYWRtaW4iLCJlbWFpbCI6ImFkbWluQGJvb2tzLnRlc3QifQ.UQgLb9jfmxQQPN_oFphv6zKW6AQU_J36VcB_mBdalWI

{ "title": "AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA", "author": "Test", "year": 2024 }

# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# 6. CORS — only origins in CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS get credentials
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### Pre-flight from an allowed origin
OPTIONS {{host}}/api/books
Origin: http://localhost:5173
Access-Control-Request-Method: POST

### Pre-flight from a hostile origin (no Allow-Origin set to it)
OPTIONS {{host}}/api/books
Origin: http://attacker.example
Access-Control-Request-Method: POST

